node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by DOVE on September 13, 2021 tagging @theuntitledmagazine. May be art of 1 person and standing.

node.text: stopped by the Innovative Exhibit on my way to the VMAs to celebrate my cover launch of their new collectors print edition and to see all the mind blowing artworks by all my new favorite contemporary/futurist artists. nothing more exciting to me than the fusion between personal art / stretching the “human” boundary / evolution of technology and what it means to move forward as a creative in this increasingly terrifying new reality. so even though i already bought 1/2 the exhibit to paper my new walls with, you can stop in to see INNOVATE until october 2nd to experience it for yourself
